{"word":"ἠβαιός","slug":"ἠβαιός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46578\" key=\"h)baio/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἠβαιός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ά</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, lon. (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cypr.</author> </bibl> acc. to <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ AB\">AB</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1095</biblScope> </bibl>) for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βαιός</foreign>, <sense id=\"n46578.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">small</tr_>, usu. with neg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδέ, οὔ οἱ ἔνι φρένες, οὐδ᾽ ἠβαιαί</foreign> no sense is in him, no not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the least</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:141\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.141</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:21:288\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.288</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔ οἱ ἔνι τρίχες, οὐδ᾽ ἠβαιαί</foreign> no not even <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a few</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:355\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.355</biblScope> </bibl>; also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠβαιὴν οὔτι κατὰ πρόφασιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg001:540\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">540</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: rarely without neg., [<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πηλαμύδες] καὶ ἠβαιαί περ ἐοῦσαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:514\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.514</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n46578.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> often in neut. as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδ᾽ ἠβαιόν</foreign> not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in the least</tr_>, not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">at all</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:380\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.380</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.14</biblScope></bibl>, etc., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phylarch.</author> </bibl>(?)<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1609.tlg001:84J\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">84J.</biblScope> </bibl>: rarely without a neg., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἠβαιὸν ἀπὸ σπείους</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a little</tr_> from the cave, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:462\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.462</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}